query:
SELECT b.bookingNumber, b.status, b.createdAt, b.customerId, u.name as userName, cp.companyName 
FROM bookings b 
LEFT JOIN users u ON b.customerId = u.id 
LEFT JOIN customer_profiles cp ON u.id = cp.userId 
WHERE b.bookingNumber = 'CAMA-20260104-542';
